Congratulations @dianamadison 
・・・
Celebrating 4 years of @dianamadisonbeauty 💜 and the launch of my latest product Cleansed. A Gingko plant gel cleanser infused with lavender oil. 

This journey with the beauty brand has been so beautiful. From the first day I launched, my amazing community here on Instagram has been supporting the growth with your love and support. In 4 years, our brand has grown into retail stores @revolve @naimies @neimanmarcus and @macys . We are getting ready to launch at another retailer in October. Stay tuned for the announcement.

When I launched @dianamadisonbeauty my goal was to create #cleanbeauty that hydrated my dry and sensitive skin. I didn’t anticipate the brand to have the success that it has today. I just needed a product that solved a problem, dry skin. Excited for what’s ahead as we get ready to launch more products using exotic ingredients from all over the world that heal. 

A big thank you to the amazing people I worked with below who helped me make this party come alive in such a short period of time.

Last night @chrisbrownofficial gifted his friends and family a night out to experience 11 eras of CB with some never seen before memorabilia and the opportunity to listen to his new album, 1111. Take a quick walk around inside with us and peek at some of the magic! 

🎧Customized virtual reality with @los_virtuality 
🎧Delicious mocktails from @icedabove 
🎧An insane 11 album content studio with @edlt.photo 
🎧Bites from @wingsnwaffles 
🎧Sounds by @jaemurphy 
🎧Furniture from @create_eventdesign 
🎧Video from @von_jackson 
🎧Desserts from @belladonnasweets 
🎧Bar by @crystal_bartenders 

Thank you to everyone that pulled this off for us so quickly. To my team on lighting, sound, production, admin, we did it and I didn’t strangle anyone 🤫

And @thecourts congratulations to you and the team.  Your love and commitment to all you’ve done with him was shown and honored and I see why he appreciates you so. 

Bouba and Ant, thank you always.

What a celebration!
